<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/51201ANJTLKTPNSNHSSNGJHMCPQDDDKRV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Be WELL, Burger & Bevy Fundraiser";
  schema:description """
	Please join us on May 26th for our 3rd annual <span class=\"BoldText\"><span class=\"ItalicText\">Be WELL, Burger and Bevy Fundraiser,</span></span> kindly hosted by Fifty Parallel Tap & Grill. Bring your friends, family, or coworkers and enjoy a delicious dinner and beverage, and a fun night including our online silent auction where you can keep bidding from your table, a 50/50 draw, and locally donated door prizes.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Upper Island Counselling is a nonprofit society providing no cost counselling and wellness benefits to businesses and organizations in Campbell River and the Upper Island for 38 years. In the last five to ten years, demand for counselling services has seen a significant increase. The number of clients and counselling sessions that we hold at no cost through our partnerships with local employers has doubled. This, combined with rising costs, has led us to new fundraising initiatives like this event. We appreciate your support and look forward to seeing you there! <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.uics.ca\">www.uics.ca</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $40.00 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
