<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/54801ALMQKJGDVBDJQKPLMBMQRRRSMCNM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Bourne to be Ozz";
  schema:description """
	Prepare for a night drenched in heavy riffs, haunting melodies, and the unmistakable spirit of metal’s earliest pioneers. Our Ozzy Osbourne and Black Sabbath tribute show brings the raw power of these legendary catalogs to life with crushing guitars, booming rhythms, and vocals that channel the Prince of Darkness himself.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>You’ll hear the iconic Sabbath classics that shaped the genre, along with the high‑energy solo hits that turned Ozzy into a metal icon. From dark, sludgy grooves to wild, adrenaline‑fueled anthems, this show delivers the full spectrum of what made these songs unforgettable.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you’re a lifelong fan or discovering the magic of these tracks on stage for the first time, expect an immersive, loud, and electrifying celebration of the godfathers of heavy metal.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets:$ 48.00 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-10-31T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
