<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/42001AQJJQTSKLLKMRKNHHDRNVHRLPNPB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Colin James Blues Trio";
  schema:description """
	The legendary Colin James returns to the Tidemark Theatre in 2026 for an unforgettable night of live blues.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With more than 30 years on stage, Colin James is one of Canada’s most celebrated blues and rock musicians. His career includes 21 studio albums, six JUNO Awards, multiple Maple Blues Awards and collaborations with some of the most influential artists in the world. From the prairies of Saskatchewan to international stages, his impact on the Canadian music scene is undeniable.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Known for his high-energy performances and signature guitar style, Colin James continues to captivate audiences of all ages. The Colin James Blues Trio features musicians Kenny Neal and Chris Caddell, creating a powerful, intimate trio experience that highlights the heart and soul of contemporary blues.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every visit to the Tidemark sells out quickly - don’t miss your chance to be part of this incredible night.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $60.00 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
