<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/55201ACQGLDNVCCMPJHCCRNVTBRTNQTQG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Genre Shuffle";
  schema:description """
	Get ready for an unforgettable evening of rhythm, movement, and pure joy! “Genre Shuffle” is a vibrant dance showcase that brings together a dynamic mix of styles—from high-energy hip-hop and graceful ballet to expressive contemporary and electrifying jazz. Each performance highlights the unique artistry and passion of the dancers, creating a colorful tapestry of music and motion.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Perfect for all ages, this family-friendly show offers something for everyone, blending exciting choreography with uplifting storytelling and plenty of feel-good moments. Whether you’re a longtime dance enthusiast or simply looking for a fun night out with loved ones, this celebration of dance promises to entertain, inspire, and leave you smiling long after the final bow. Get your tickets today before they sell out!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $34.50 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Babes in Arms:</span> Each person <span class=\"BoldText\">REGARDLESS OF AGE</span> must have a valid ticket to enter a performance. If you have an infant <span class=\"BoldText\">under the age of two</span> who will be sitting on your lap, please let our Box Office know and we will issue a complimentary ticket for your infant. All persons age two and up must have paid admission.</span>
""";
