<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/48401AVGNMMHRQVCLVRTRPKGHCJLGDVKR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "GOT STONES! Steel Wheels Tour";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">GOT STONES!</span> – A High-Voltage Tribute to the Rolling Stones’ Steel Wheels Era<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready to relive one of the Rolling Stones’ most iconic eras as <span class=\"BoldText\">GOT STONES! </span>brings the electrifying energy of the Steel Wheels Tour back to life. Celebrating the Stones’ triumphant late-’80s return to the stage, <span class=\"BoldText\">GOT STONES! </span>delivers the swagger, sound, and spectacle of this legendary tour with striking authenticity.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From the driving pulse of Mixed Emotions and Sad Sad Sad to the timeless anthems Gimme Shelter, Start Me Up, and Jumpin’ Jack Flash, the band recreates the power and polish of the Steel Wheels experience—complete with the sharp riffs, soulful backing vocals, and stadium-ready attitude that defined the era.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With spot-on vocals, searing guitars, and a rhythm section built to shake the room, <span class=\"BoldText\">GOT STONES!</span> captures the magic of the Rolling Stones at full force. Whether you lived through the original tour or are discovering it anew, this is your chance to witness the raw excitement, style, and sound that made Steel Wheels a milestone in rock history.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">GOT STONES!</span>: The ultimate celebration of the Rolling Stones’ Steel Wheels Tour—live, loud, and rolling right through you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $47.60 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+ applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
