<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/53801AKGMPDLHTQMBLGCMLLSBPRBQDTHL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Alan Jackson Experience";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">The Alan Jackson Experience</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Performed by Aaron Halliday, a two-time ISSA Entertainer of the Year Award winner and Canadian/ Nashville recording artist, and presented by ASH Entertainment, brings an internationally recognized tribute to Alan Jackson, featuring Award-winning musicians.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This show is a precise recreation of an Alan Jackson concert, boasting an authentic look, stage presence, and sound that will transport you to the real thing. Prepare yourself for an energetic and entertaining performance that will have you singing along to 'Good Time' and reminiscing about the past with 'Remember When.'<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>As an added bonus, ticket holders can meet the artists in the lobby during intermission.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Check out link  below to get a feel for the show:<span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://youtu.be/Fyr8POiW08M?si=ynHlUvr-tpNWPi1Z\">https://youtu.be/Fyr8POiW08M?si=ynHlUvr-tpNWPi1Z</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $57.00 Adult, $53.00 Senior/Student <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
